{"tid":801643,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"(忽發奇想) 其實香港有冇可能搞到個自己嘅produce 101","createTime":"2018-08-31T20:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T01:25:37.000Z","uid":86729,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"315c24358f54c3e0872353d0afb2897f0d7b03da","tid":801643,"uid":86729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T20:07:30.000Z","msg":"追過創造101同啱啱final咗嘅produce48<br />\n雖然呢啲節目好多內幕，一路睇一路好想香港都有啲咁好睇嘅選秀睇吓(唔好同我講全民造星)。<br />\n其實之前有一排(大約8 9年前)都興過台灣果隻歌唱比賽，香港都做得起。<br />\n香港都有唔少唱片公司，仲有好多舞團之類。咁其實呢類紀錄片式選秀都可以試吓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> FF得過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  算鳩數把喇<br />\n<br />\n<ins>無限FF導師團</ins><br />\n全民監製代表︰農夫？<br />\n歌唱老師︰(女) 容祖兒？Gin Lee？呀漿？(男) 張敬軒？古巨基？陳奕迅？<br />\n舞蹈老師︰莊綻欣？狄易達？High King？草蜢？(我相信郭富城睬你都傻)<br />\nRAP老師︰MC Jin？農夫？"},{"pid":"fc64a76667a928f5d7f98c9d78480b755709f230","tid":801643,"uid":48577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T21:05:47.000Z","msg":"你4pick都中3個啦"},{"pid":"397727a779a2f9c8e23e15d84c8d9cf8e58ae6bd","tid":801643,"uid":70527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T22:29:13.000Z","msg":"全民造星已經好似啦wor"},{"pid":"aabb57b67ad858fe9bd794ea5457f70bde86b761","tid":801643,"uid":12432,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T23:34:33.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩 最後咪又係黑箱作業"},{"pid":"133c68ab45e7f9f2488881804081ebec4aca2259","tid":801643,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:25:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}